snippet.title: Johnny depp and Amber heard Full Controversy Explained
snippet.description:
In today’s video we are going to explain the full controversy between the ex couple. 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
____________________________________________

In May 2016, Amber Heard filed for divorce from Johnny Depp, whom she married in a lavish island ceremony in February 2015. Although the couple had seemed happy  Amber also filed a restraining order against the 53-year-old actor, which included allegations of domestic abuse.
